import React from 'react'
import { Image, TouchableOpacity } from 'react-native'
import {  View, FormControl, Stack, Input, Box, Flex } from 'native-base'

export default function Display() {
  return <Box w="90%" maxWidth="300px" flex='1'>
      <FormControl>
        <Stack mx="4">
          <FormControl.Label fontWeight={'bold'}>Dis</FormControl.Label>
          <Input bg='primary.50' borderRadius={'10px'} height={'100px'} />
        </Stack>
      </FormControl>
        <Flex direction='row'>
            <TouchableOpacity>
                <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 2.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 1 (1).png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 3.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </Flex>
            <Flex direction='row' justifyContent='center' marginRight={'20px'}>
            <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 4.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
                <TouchableOpacity>
                    <Image style={{width: 70, height: 70, marginTop: 20, marginLeft:20}} source={require('../assets/Group 5.png')}/>
                </TouchableOpacity>
            </Flex>
    </Box>
}
